{"tid":2362000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩子探黎智英：唔經唔覺剩10秒","createTime":"2021-01-11T06:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T08:49:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"01fe49513590e28dddef79295302634702da8e9d","tid":2362000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/6RKSQ4RDBNFN3F26MDHYLK5KZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2F6RKSQ4RDBNFN3F26MDHYLK5KZQ%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=ff6c538c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2F6RKSQ4RDBNFN3F26MDHYLK5KZQ%2F&h=842d81cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/6RKSQ4RDBNFN3F26MDHYLK5KZQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n兩子探黎智英：唔經唔覺剩10秒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0Fi45dKBwXxw0BUVAvZT5FV-jV4=/851x455/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AIJIJHHFFFAL7LZK7QSBTL5G4A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0Fi45dKBwXxw0BUVAvZT5FV-jV4%3D%2F851x455%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAIJIJHHFFFAL7LZK7QSBTL5G4A.png&h=d90653d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎見恩（左）及黎耀恩（右）昨指父親黎智英（右圖）精神不錯。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港天文台連日發出寒冷天氣警告，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台議員：黎代表港人對自由渴望<br />\n<br />\n昨晨8時，黎見恩與黎耀恩抵達荔枝角收押所，未有攜帶任何物品入內，逗留約一個半小時後，約9時20分離去，二人表現輕鬆。<br />\n<br />\n長子黎見恩表示，父親精神不錯，有足夠保暖衣物，並笑稱「佢話仲可以着襪㖭！」黎見恩又說，主要與父親閒話家常，父子話題多，未有談及香港局勢，時間不知不覺流逝，「唔經唔覺剩番10秒（探望時間）」。<br />\n<br />\n台北市議員王世堅昨發信聲援黎智英，指他對媒體的堅持、對言論自由的捍衞，代表的不是他個人，而是所有香港人對自由的渴望。他又指港府剝奪了黎的人身自由，更摧殘了香港人民的言論自由，如今不僅只是黎被鐵鏈綑綁，而是整個香港被中國共產黨禁錮。<br />\n<br />\n王世堅指出，鄧小平的「50年不變」猶如昨日所言，卻昨是今非，此時正是香港民主最黑暗時刻。但他形容，黎明來臨前的夜晚總是最黑暗，世界已看到香港人的堅韌，相信香港自由的曙光，會再次照亮每位港人。"},{"pid":"366cb04822c68b1ea8b38eea0d68976c42a9bdda","tid":2362000,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"黃豬唔好再搞港獨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎生 香港人唔會忘記你嘅付出 你安心入去坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎智英：港獨當年係有鬼背後推動， 當時我已經叫唔好中計！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"248e2b3b1d8c54f70f7f9f6e6e127a69811dea6f","tid":2362000,"uid":281492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"366cb04822c68b1ea8b38eea0d68976c42a9bdda","tid":2362000,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"黃豬唔好再搞港獨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎生 香港人唔會忘記你嘅付出 你安心入去坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎智英：港獨當年係有鬼背後推動， 當時我已經叫唔好中計！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦垃圾"},{"pid":"276ba255e1cc66a517f5fe47ea94f0b25b4aa47b","tid":2362000,"uid":223428,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"248e2b3b1d8c54f70f7f9f6e6e127a69811dea6f","tid":2362000,"uid":281492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"366cb04822c68b1ea8b38eea0d68976c42a9bdda","tid":2362000,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"黃豬唔好再搞港獨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎生 香港人唔會忘記你嘅付出 你安心入去坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎智英：港獨當年係有鬼背後推動， 當時我已經叫唔好中計！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦垃圾"},"citedBy":